import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import './navigation-links1.css' const NavigationLinks1 = (props) => { return (
{props.text} {props.text1} {props.text2} {props.text3} {props.text4}
) } NavigationLinks1.defaultProps = { text3: 'Team', text: 'About', text1: 'Features', text4: 'Blog', text2: 'Pricing', rootClassName: '', } NavigationLinks1.propTypes = { text3: PropTypes.string, text: PropTypes.string, text1: PropTypes.string, text4: PropTypes.string, text2: PropTypes.string, rootClassName: PropTypes.string, } export default NavigationLinks1
